//%attributes = {}
/* Purpose: true when this method is called in the context of a component
 ------------------
I_am_a_component ()
 Created by: Kirk Brooks as Designer, Created: 07/11/26, 17:52:53

 In a component, Structure file (no *) is the component's own file and
 Structure file(*) is the host's — they differ. Standalone they are equal.
*/

#DECLARE : Boolean
return Structure file#Structure file(*)
